2-02 21:23:22','2023-12-02 21:23:22','Active'),(7,'Move Out Cleaning','33','/images/service/move_out_cleaning.jpg','Leave your old place spotless with our Move Out Cleaning service. Our specialist, Diana, ensures a thorough cleaning for a smooth transition to the next chapter, providing you peace of mind.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:23:49','2023-12-02 21:23:49','Active'),(8,'Vacation Rental Cleaning','31','/images/service/vacation_rental_cleaning.jpg','Ensure your vacation rental property is guest-ready with our Vacation Rental Cleaning service. Frank is here to deliver a clean and welcoming space for every guest\'s enjoyable stay.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:25:48','2023-12-02 21:25:48','Active'),(9,'Garage Cleaning','30','/images/service/garage_cleaning.jpg','Transform your garage into a functional and tidy area with our Garage Cleaning service. Henry is here to declutter and organize your space, ensuring a clean and organized environment.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:26:06','2023-12-02 21:26:06','Active'),(10,'One Time Cleaning Services','32','/images/service/one_time_cleaning_services.jpg','Make your space shine with our One Time Cleaning Services. We specializes in providing a thorough and refreshing clean, whether it\'s for a special occasion or just a simple refresh.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:26:35','2023-12-02 21:26:35','Active'),(11,'Car Washing','26','/images/service/car_washing.jpg','Give your vehicle the care it deserves with our Car Washing service. Jack is here to ensure your car not only looks great but also feels great with a clean and well-maintained appearance.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:26:46','2023-12-02 21:26:46','Active'),(12,'Laundry Help','27','/images/service/laundry_help.jpg','Enjoy more free time as Karen takes care of your laundry needs with our Laundry Help service. From washing to folding, Karen is your specialist for a hassle-free laundry experience.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:26:53','2023-12-02 21:26:53','Active'),(13,'Pressure Washing','34','/images/service/pressure_washing.jpg','Restore your surfaces to their original beauty with our Pressure Washing service. Leo specializes in giving your exteriors a thorough clean, ensuring a fresh and well-maintained look.','Cleaning Services','2023-12-02 21:27:19','2023-12-02 21:27:19','Active'),(14,'Painting and Decorating','40','/images/service/painting_decorating.jpg','Transform your space with our Painting and Decorating service. Whether you\'re looking to refresh the colors of your walls or add creative touches to enhance the aesthetics, our skilled professionals are here to bring your vision to life.','Decorating and Painting','2023-12-02 21:27:39','2023-12-02 21:27:39','Active'),(15,'Backyard Painting','45','/images/service/backyard_painting.jpg','Enhance your outdoor space with charm and color through our Backyard Painting service. Let\'s create a backyard oasis together that reflects your personal style.','Decorating and Painting','2023-12-02 21:27:47','2023-12-02 21:27:47','Active'),(16,'Interior Design','50','/images/service/interior_design.jpg','Bring style and functionality to your interiors with our Interior Design service. Make your space uniquely yours with the expertise of our professionals.','Decorating and Painting','2023-12-02 21:27:58','2023-12-02 21:27:58','Active'),(17,'Canvas Paint Service','35','/images/service/canvas_paint_service.jpg','Experience our Canvas Paint Service, bringing your ideas to life on canvas. Whether it\'s a custom artwork or a themed painting, our professionals ensure a personalized touch.','Decorating and Painting','2023-12-02 21:28:17','2023-12-02 21:28:17','Active'),(18,'Electrical Work','35','/images/service/electrical_work.jpg','Ensure the safety and functionality of your electrical systems with our Electrical Work service. Our expert professionals, led by Sarah, handle installations and troubleshoot any electrical issues to keep your space secure.','Electrical Services','2023-12-02 21:28:28','2023-12-02 21:28:28','Active'),(19,'Plumbing','50','/images/service/plumbing.jpg','Experience top-notch plumbing solutions with our Plumbing service. Led by David, we provide comprehensive services, from fixing leaks to installing new fixtures, ensuring your plumbing system is in excellent condition.','Plumbing Services','2023-12-02 21:28:46','2023-12-02 21:28:46','Active'),(20,'Furniture Assembly','30','/images/service/furniture_assembly.jpg','Efficiently handle your furniture assembly needs with our Furniture Assembly service. Jessica, our expert assembler, ensures precision in assembling your furniture, be it a new purchase or a relocation.','Furniture Assembly','2023-12-02 21:28:54','2023-12-02 21:28:54','Active'),(21,'Couch Assembly','35','/images/service/couch_assembly.jpg','Relax and let us take care of your Couch Assembly needs. Andrew, our specialist, will assemble your sofa with care and expertise, ensuring a comfortable and perfectly assembled seating arrangement.','Furniture Assembly','2023-12-02 21:29:22','2023-12-02 21:29:22','Active'),(22,'Wardrobe Assembly','32','/images/service/wardrobe_assembly.jpg','Assemble and organize your wardrobe with our Wardrobe Assembly service, ensuring a sturdy and functional storage solution.','Furniture Assembly','2023-12-02 21:30:04','2023-12-02 21:30:04','Active'),(23,'Table Assembly','28','/images/service/table_assembly.jpg','Specializing in Table Assembly, we\'ll assemble your dining tables to coffee tables with precision, ensuring a stable and elegant finish.','Furniture Assembly','2023-12-02 21:30:24','2023-12-02 21:30:24','Active'),(24,'Disassemble Furniture','25','/images/service/disassemble_furniture.jpg','Carefully dismantle your furniture for relocation or storage with our Disassemble Furniture services. We ensure each part is handled with care.','Furniture Assembly','2023-12-02 21:30:57','2023-12-02 21:30:57','Active'),(25,'Smart Home Installation','45','/images/service/smart_home_installation.jpg','Upgrade your home with the latest technology using our Smart Home Installation service. From smart thermostats to security systems, we seamlessly integrate them into your living space.','Assembly and Installation','2023-12-02 21:31:12','2023-12-02 21:31:12','Active'),(26,'Cabinet Installation','40','/images/service/cabinet_installation.jpg','Upgrade your kitchen or bathroom with our Cabinet Installation service. We ensure precise installation for a functional and stylish space.','Assembly and Installation','2023-12-02 21:31:35','2023-12-02 21:31:35','Active'),(27,'Carpentry Services','50','/images/service/carpentry_services.jpg','Enhance your home with our Carpentry Services. From custom woodworking to repairs, we bring craftsmanship and attention to detail to every project.','Carpentry Services','2023-12-02 21:31:43','2023-12-02 21:31:43','Active'),(28,'Heavy Lifting','35','/images/service/heavy_lifting.jpg','Handle the lifting and moving tasks with our Heavy Lifting service. We ensure a safe and efficient process for your belongings.','Heavy Lifting and Moving','2023-12-02 21:31:50','2023-12-02 21:31:50','Active'),(29,'Help Moving','40','/images/service/help_moving.jpg','Make your move stress-free with our Help Moving service. We\'ll provide assistance with packing, loading, and unloading, ensuring a smooth transition to your new home.','Heavy Lifting and Moving','2023-12-02 21:32:31','2023-12-02 21:32:31','Active'),(30,'Yard Work Services','25','/images/service/yard_work.jpg','Maintain a beautiful outdoor space with our Yard Work Services. From lawn mowing to garden care, we provide the expertise to keep your yard looking its best.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:32:41','2023-12-02 21:32:41','Active'),(31,'Gardening Services','28','/images/service/gardening_services.jpg','Nurture your plants and create a vibrant and flourishing garden with our Gardening Services. Elijah is here to bring expertise to your outdoor space.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:32:49','2023-12-02 21:32:49','Active'),(32,'Lawn Care Services','30','/images/service/lawn_care.jpg','Isabella offers Lawn Care Services to ensure your lawn stays healthy and green. Regular care is provided to keep it in top condition.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:32:56','2023-12-02 21:32:56','Active'),(34,'Tree Trimming Service','32','/images/service/tree_trimming.jpg','This service offers expert Tree Trimming, ensuring the health and appearance of your trees for a picturesque landscape.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:34:10','2023-12-02 21:34:10','Active'),(35,'Fence Installation & Repair Services','35','/images/service/fence_installation.jpg','This service provides expertise in Fence Installation & Repair. Whether it\'s installation or repairs, the goal is to ensure your fence stands strong and looks great.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:34:22','2023-12-02 21:34:22','Active'),(36,'Fence Staining','29','/images/service/fence_staining.jpg','Specializing in Fence Staining, this service enhances the durability and aesthetics of your fence with professional staining services.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:34:32','2023-12-02 21:34:32','Active'),(37,'Lawn Fertilizer Service','27','/images/service/lawn_fertilizer.jpg','Offering Lawn Fertilizer Service, this service provides the nutrients your lawn needs for lush, healthy growth.','Yard and Outdoor Services','2023-12-02 21:34:42','2023-12-02 21:34:42','Active');
